45
00:10:28,337 --> 00:10:29,099
Pardon ?

46
00:10:29,338 --> 00:10:30,363
Baisse la main !

47
00:10:36,980 --> 00:10:39,278
Rengaine ton arme. Je le veux vivant.

48
